OL,3,CPanel retires to consider whether
OL,4,Cpolice officer called others 'cotton
OL,5,Cpickers'
OL,7,FA misconduct panel in the case of a
OL,8,FMetropolitan police officer who is
OL,9,Falleged to have used the term "cotton
OL,10,Fpickers" to describe black officers
OL,11,Fhas retired to consider its decision.
OL,13,FPc Mia Korell, who is part of the
OL,14,FRoads and Transport policing command,
OL,15,Fallegedly used the term to describe
OL,16,Fblack officers who did not believe the
OL,17,FTerritorial Support Group (TSG) was a
OL,18,Fracist unit.
