OL,3,CPanel retires to consider whether
OL,4,Cpolice officer called others 'cotton
OL,5,Cpickers'
OL,7,FIt is alleged Pc Korell, herself a
OL,8,Fblack officer, used the language when
OL,9,Fshe bumped into Inspector Alistair
OL,10,FPhillips while they were both off duty
OL,11,Fin Guildford on October 7 2022.
OL,13,FThe pair had a broader conversation
OL,14,Fbefore they began speaking about
OL,15,Fracism in policing, the misconduct
OL,16,Fpanel heard.
OL,18,FAfter hearing evidence from Mr
OL,19,FPhillips and Pc Korell on Monday, the
OL,20,Fpanel heard from lawyers representing
OL,21,Fthe Metropolitan Police and Pc Korell.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
