OL,3,CPanel retires to consider whether
OL,4,Cpolice officer called others 'cotton
OL,5,Cpickers'
OL,7,FChloe Hill, on behalf of the Met, told
OL,8,Fthe panel sitting in central London
OL,9,Fduring her closing speech: "The
OL,10,Foutcome of this is that the panel have
OL,11,Fto make a decision on the credibility
OL,12,Fof the two witnesses."
OL,14,F"It (cotton pickers) is so specific
OL,15,Fand unusual it is highly unlikely that
OL,16,FInspector Phillips misheard," Ms Hill
OL,17,Fadded.
