OL,3,CPanel retires to consider whether
OL,4,Cpolice officer called others 'cotton
OL,5,Cpickers'
OL,7,F"This self-evidently amounts to gross
OL,8,Fmisconduct in that it is conduct so
OL,9,Fserious that it can amount to
OL,10,Fdismissal."
OL,12,FEarlier on Monday, Mr Phillips told
OL,13,Fthe hearing Pc Korell asked him if he
OL,14,Fbelieved the TSG, which both officers
OL,15,Fwere part of at the time, was racist,
OL,16,Fto which he said no.
OL,18,FMr Phillips said it was then that Pc
OL,19,FKorell said black TSG officers who do
OL,20,Fnot agree that the TSG is a racist
OL,21,Funit are "just cotton pickers".
