OL,3,CPanel retires to consider whether
OL,4,Cpolice officer called others 'cotton
OL,5,Cpickers'
OL,7,FPc Korell denied using the term
OL,8,F"cotton pickers" and told the panel:
OL,9,F"It is not a term that you hear often
OL,10,Fin conversation, it is not part of my
OL,11,Fvernacular.
OL,13,F"I am aware of its existence but I
OL,14,Fdidn't say it, it strikes me as odd."
OL,16,FRebecca Hadgett, representing Pc
OL,17,FKorell, told the hearing: "This is
OL,18,Fclearly a straightforward factual
OL,19,Fdispute, whether the words were used
OL,20,For not."
