OL,3,CPanel retires to consider whether
OL,4,Cpolice officer called others 'cotton
OL,5,Cpickers'
OL,7,FShe asked the panel, chaired by
OL,8,FCommander Jason Prins, to consider
OL,9,Fwhat sort of person Pc Korell is and
OL,10,Fthe evidence of her character, citing
OL,11,Fher "hard work, dedication and
OL,12,Fpassion".
OL,14,FThe panel is expected to return its
OL,15,Fdecision on Tuesday.
